data.description: Stunning newer 4 bedroom home in the Elks area. This beautiful home was built 2022 and  has high ceilings, quartz counters throughout, upgraded glass backsplash, gray cabinets, stainless steel GE appliances. Double sink vanity in owners suite bathroom along with a walk in shower and walk in closet. Guest bathroom has double sinks with a tub/shower combo. Xeriscaped front and backyard for easy maintenance. Very well maintained and completely ready for the new owners to enjoy.
